{
    var newProgress = initial+'px';
    $(id).style.backgroundPosition=newProgress+' 0';
    setText(id,'0');
}

*
\************************************************************/

{
    var nowWidth = $(id).style.backgroundPosition.split("px");
    return (Math.floor(100+(nowWidth[0]/eachPercent))+'%');
